<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5"><b>Voices of Socialism 2007</b></font><p>
<font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">June 22, 2007 | Pages 9 to 12</font><p>

<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><i>Socialist Worker </i>prints brief excerpts from a few of the nearly 100 discussions held at Socialism 2007.<p>

<A HREF="#Klein"><b>Margarita Klein</b> | Grassroots Strategies for Defending Immigrant Rights</A><BR>
<A HREF="#Taylor"><b>Keeanga-Yamahtta Taylor</b> | Black Reconstruction: America's Unfinished Revolution</A><BR>
